431
00:20:57,000 --> 00:21:00,458
And so, having fulfilled
her master's destiny,

432
00:21:00,541 --> 00:21:04,875
Laurie, the Grand First
Assistroid, left Earth forever.

433
00:21:09,458 --> 00:21:10,666
So, what...?

434
00:21:10,750 --> 00:21:12,625
You decided to leave
everything up to Kio?

435
00:21:12,708 --> 00:21:13,833
I did.

436
00:21:13,916 --> 00:21:15,291
What a pity...

437
00:21:15,375 --> 00:21:17,541
Laurie's a living witness
to history, you know?

438
00:21:17,625 --> 00:21:20,458
I feel so ashamed.

439
00:21:20,541 --> 00:21:22,583
This was pretty
special for you, Kio.

440
00:21:22,666 --> 00:21:24,291
Probably won't
ever happen again.

441
00:21:24,375 --> 00:21:25,833
But where will
Laurie go now...?

442
00:21:25,916 --> 00:21:26,833
Back to Catia?

443
00:21:26,916 --> 00:21:28,166
Sadly, no.

444
00:21:28,250 --> 00:21:30,125
Her remaining
operational time--

445
00:21:30,208 --> 00:21:31,541
her life that is -

446
00:21:31,625 --> 00:21:33,250
won't last much longer.

447
