without being recalled are
given two basic options:

450
00:21:43,041 --> 00:21:44,875
choose another master
or refuse measures

451
00:21:44,958 --> 00:21:46,833
that will prolong
their life.

452
00:21:46,916 --> 00:21:49,958
And Laurie...?
