453
00:21:50,041 --> 00:21:52,291
Hang on... How much
time does she have?

454
00:21:52,375 --> 00:21:55,291
Could be as little as
less than half a cycle...

455
00:21:55,375 --> 00:21:57,958
The lifetime of her biological
parts is indefinite...

456
00:21:58,041 --> 00:22:00,250
With the new models
we know exactly.

457
00:22:00,333 --> 00:22:02,958
But with Laurie,
only time will tell.

458
00:22:03,041 --> 00:22:06,291
Typhoon seventeen is now over
the Pacific, moving north,

459
00:22:06,375 --> 00:22:10,833
roughly four hundred kilometers
south of Ishigaki Island.

460
00:22:15,875 --> 00:22:18,208
The little ones
are so lucky.

461
00:22:23,791 --> 00:22:25,125
