465
00:22:36,750 --> 00:22:38,833
Yeah, please.

466
00:22:38,916 --> 00:22:40,500
Thanks a lot.

467
00:22:40,583 --> 00:22:42,291
Friend.

468
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:59,541
Captain, I...
thank you for this.

469
00:22:59,625 --> 00:23:01,708
