Earth as long as I can.

470
00:23:01,791 --> 00:23:03,250
I understand...

471
00:23:03,333 --> 00:23:06,708
This planet is just as special
to us, as it is to you.

472
00:23:06,791 --> 00:23:07,958
By the way...

473
00:23:08,041 --> 00:23:09,458
There's a song
I'd like to listen

474
00:23:09,541 --> 00:23:11,041
to while
we admire the view.

475
00:23:11,125 --> 00:23:12,250
That okay?

476
00:23:12,333 --> 00:23:13,833
Yes...

477
00:23:13,916 --> 00:23:16,791
Actually, I was just thinking
of asking you the same thing.

478
00:25:25,666 --> 00:25:27,875
It's Christmas time,
so what's up?

479
00:25:27,958 --> 00:25:30,125
Catians learning about
Santa Claus and stuff!

480
00:25:30,208 --> 00:25:31,875
Of course, nothing
says holiday spirit

481
00:25:31,958 --> 00:25:34,708
like a bunch of evil space
dogs attacking your home!

482
00:25:34,791 --> 00:25:36,875
Next time...!
"We Came After You!"

483
00:25:36,958 --> 00:25:39,500
I'm coming
to drop in on you!

